{"tid":1886844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[喜事全面進場]支那政法委發通知稱激發正能量要有更多有溫度有淚點暖新聞","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:34:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b93f04d076e360a421bd4fe4c9c4869109a6c4e3","tid":1886844,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"中央政法委就防控疫情相關工作向政法系統發有關通知，表示要激發社會正能量，推出更多有溫度、有淚點、有人情味的「暖新聞」，為打贏疫情防控戰營造良好輿論氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n通知指出要注重整合政法、社會和媒體資源，集中宣傳政法系統在防控疫情、維護安全穩定中湧現的感人事跡。<br />\n<br />\n通知亦要求大力宣傳執法和司法人員等，依法打擊妨害疫情防控的違法犯罪行為，妥善化解疫情矛盾糾紛等。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509465-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509465-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=877a7fd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509465-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3cc28abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509465-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ae4fQ5gPlis/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fae4fQ5gPlis%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=0b2b10e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59c208e1c8b94df864930bf93889f23f5baaa86f","tid":1886844,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n日日集體燒死人<br />\n死之前仲要唱紅歌？<br />\n你地黨係咪精神病吖屌你？？<br />\n連死都要為黨死得好吖？"},{"pid":"b722e91c4f6fba7627fe98888dd6ab08b67f83fc","tid":1886844,"uid":3860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"唔怪得共產黨成個丁蟹咁<br />\n<br />\n打感動都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec5ca23b23ccc0a2a4ac1d28de368494ff82ce","tid":1886844,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"他全家開開心心的死光了, 夠晒正能量"},{"pid":"6071975d17bafd391ad07b5bb9f81ed2a4bb1356","tid":1886844,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"白事當喜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c525618153480ff95269d8de9a66ef711342ba1","tid":1886844,"uid":321345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"內地抗疫報道神情節 出生僅 20 日嬰兒懂喊「媽媽在哪」 網民狠批 陸媒道歉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38CCSjd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38CCSjd&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=333198c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38CCSjd</a><br />\n<br />\n「大年初一（上月25日）凌晨3時，王慧將出生不到20天的雙胞胎兒子哄睡，讓丈夫雍波開車將她從洋縣送回西京醫院。」其後，雍波回到家中，「剛起床不久兩個孩子稚氣地問：『媽媽幹嘛去了？』雍波哄着說：媽媽上班班了，回來給你們買糖糖」。<br />\n<br />\n出生不到 20 人的孩子，竟然懂說話，這篇報道事後在網上廣傳，內地民眾對此熱議紛紛。"},{"pid":"1b792a0599228e612f2e18c28450876db57c0938","tid":1886844,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19ec5ca23b23ccc0a2a4ac1d28de368494ff82ce","tid":1886844,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"他全家開開心心的死光了, 夠晒正能量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f8c5fb66bad237ce220cfc0c61854133d1b937","tid":1886844,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":